  Requirements:
    PHP version 4.2.3+
	MYSQL

  Summary:
    PHP login script is intended to provide the users an automated and fully
	customizable login script independent of the database integrated with
	the admin feature.
    For a summary of features, please see the Documentation.txt file.

  Download:
    You can get the newest version at  https://sourceforge.net/projects/phploginanydata

